notes: Static bundled reference for RDS cost estimation. Refresh via Claude Code + instances MCP. Monthly = hourly * 730 (rounded 6dp). Families not in MCP dataset (r8g, r8gd, t1, t2, x1, x1e, x2g, x2idn, x2iedn, x2iezn, z1d) are excluded. tpc/* and metal/* variants excluded (Oracle RAC / bare-metal only). SQL Server Web and Enterprise on-demand pricing not separately available from MCP; sqlserver_std is the best available approximation for those tiers. GovCloud (us-gov-west-1) blocks present only for confirmed-available families: t3, m5, m5d, m6g, m6gd, m6i, r3, r4, r5, r5d, r6g, r6gd, r6i, r7g, r7i. MariaDB unavailable in GovCloud t3 (null). Aurora standard unavailable in GovCloud r3 (only aurora_io). r7i GovCloud: sqlserver_std equals mysql/pg/mariadb rate at all sizes.
